Content.bodyText:
Hi Darren,  I'm interested in adding a map to the contact page of my neighbor's farm: www.cowberrycrossingfarm.com, and I've read through the posts here, but I frankly have no idea what you're all talking about, jQuery, document ready event, etc. 

Would it be possible to email me a complete example, or is there some doc somewhere that I haven't seen yet?  

Thanks! 

Marc
